CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 6, 1952, page 13, reads: "All Nationalities - Among those at this table were: John DeVito, Geraldine Lucci, Eleanor Cagan, Rose Torregrossa, Catherine Little, William Braun, Gertrude..., Marianne M. Long, Rodger Schwartz, R. Gonzales, P. Imro and Thomas Conroy. Factional supporters in Allegheny County Republican politics dined in harmony Saturday night at Syria Mosque."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait including John DeVito, Geraldine Lucci, Eleanor Cagan, Rose Torregrossa, Catherine Little, William Braun, Gertrude..., Marianne M. Long, Rodger Schwartz, R. Gonzales, P. Imro and Thomas Conroy, seated at banquet table in Syria Mosque for county Republican victory celebration
